➜小鹏上市，恒大更名，拜腾回归｜造车新势力周报
http://www.sohu.com/a/415599904_115873	15084
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200830/dad329b967fb48f8a56f6bb8e623a75c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
